snippet.title: Crime Boss: Rockay City Announcement Trailer [ESRB 4K]
snippet.description:
Introducing Crime Boss: Rockay City, an organised crime game combining FPS action and turf wars from INGAME STUDIOS.

Take on the role of Travis Baker – a man with his sights set on becoming the new King of Rockay City, one crime at a time.

Launching on the Epic Games Store on March 28th, 2023: https://505.games/CrimeBossEpic 
Coming soon to PS5 and Xbox Series X/S
